                    "value": "<p>The sea serpent extends the spines along its back and Swims or Strides. Each creature the serpent is adjacent to at any point during its movement takes [[/r {4d6+8}[slashing]]]{4d6+8 slashing damage} (<span data-pf2-check=\"reflex\" data-pf2-dc=\"32\" data-pf2-traits=\"attack,move,damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Spine Rake DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Reflex</span> save).</p>"
